<plot>"My Father's Eyes" is about a young, mixed-race American woman who meets her Asian-Indian father for the first time in her life. Set in contemporary New York, "My Father's Eyes" begins as we join Om and Linda making their final preparations before meeting each other in beautiful Fort Tryon Park in New York City. When Linda and Om meet, each receives an unexpected gift from the other, culminating in an ending that will start a new chapter in their lives.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?383783</url></doc>
